MY GPT SEARCH

| ASPECT | EVENT | ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES |
|--------|-------|----------------------|
| Changes per invocation | ✅ YES | ❌ NO |
| Set in code | ❌ NO (passed by trigger) | ✅ YES (config) |
| Access method | `event['key']` | `os.environ['KEY']` |
| Max size | 6 MB (sync) / 256 KB (async) | 4 KB (total all vars) |
| Encryption | ❌ No (plain text in logs) | ✅ Yes (KMS encryption) |
| Use for | User input, file names, request ID | Database URLs, API keys, env name |
| Security | Low | High |
| Modification | Per invocation | Requires redeploy |
| Example value | `{"user": "john", "file": "a.jpg"}` | `DATABASE_URL=postgres://...` |
